sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor U as User
participant FE as Frontend
participant AC as AuthController
participant AS as AuthService
participant BL as TokenBlocklist
participant RT as RefreshToken
participant TTL as TTL Store

U->>FE: Select logout
FE->>AC: POST /auth/logout
AC->>AS: logout(accessToken, refreshToken)
par Block access token
  AS->>BL: Add access token to blocklist
  BL->>TTL: Store token hash until expiry
  TTL-->>BL: Stored
and Revoke refresh token
  AS->>RT: Delete refresh token
  RT-->>AS: Deleted
end
AS-->>AC: Logout completed
AC-->>FE: 204 No Content
FE-->>U: Clear local authentication state
